race.comment: DOLCE DIOR (5) has raced at Group and Stakes level and will be better for her two runs back this campaign at the provincials. Has the winkers on for the first time and the numbers to be winning. ICON DREAM (9) turned in a decent effort last start to finish second over 2000m at Kembla Grange. Enjoyed the dryer surface and will jump from an inside barrier. Finds a suitable assignment and should be right in the finish. FINAL IMPACT (2) stepped up to a middle distance at Dubbo and wasn't beaten far. Finds it hard to win but that effort would see him very competitive. around the mark. HIGHLAND LAD (7) showed plenty twice at Newcastle early in his preparation but the form has tailed off. Rolls up here on a 5-day return and is one to include at a price.
